add_allowed_surface

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_allowed_surface -  Allows the npc to work on a specific surface in a room, eg.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_allowed_surface(string surface)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^surface%^RESET%^ - the name of the surface to be added

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc/surface_decorator.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Allows the npc to work on a specific surface in a room, eg. floor, ceiling
If the argument passed is "wall", they will be able to work on all walls,
eg. north wall, east wall, south wall, etc.

.EP

